{"ID":"20240723105443-uvcr53y","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20240723105443-uvcr53y","title":"yolo训练方法","type":"doc","updated":"20250325095724"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240723105449-jst2gud","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240723105449-jst2gud","updated":"20241014085250"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"流程"}]},{"ID":"20240723105516-ud366dc","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240723105516-ud366dc","updated":"20241014085250"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.安装环境"}]},{"ID":"20240723105532-qx5boch","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240723105532-qx5boch","updated":"20241014085250"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"git clone https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5\ncd yolov5\npip install -r requirements.txt\n#安装过慢用清华源更新\npip install -r requirements.txt -i https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/pypi/web/simple\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240723105443-wf4jbe3","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240723105443-wf4jbe3","updated":"20240723105620"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240723105602-rc3wx8w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240723105602-rc3wx8w","updated":"20240723105620"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"网络问题可能会一直安装失败，开加速器多下几遍"}]}]},{"ID":"20240723105620-l8cfujx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240723105620-l8cfujx","updated":"20240724093958"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.文件配置"}]},{"ID":"20240723105916-i7vaxx1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240723105916-i7vaxx1","updated":"20240724093958"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.1训练图片"}]},{"ID":"20240723105647-wwyaclt","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240723105647-wwyaclt","updated":"20240723110028"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240723105648-f1ojikc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240723105648-f1ojikc","updated":"20240723110028"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在yolov5文件夹下的data文件夹添加以下文件夹，然后把图片放入train和val，train用来训练 val用来验证"}]}]},{"ID":"20240723105812-3ezezhn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240723105812-3ezezhn","updated":"20240723105928"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"├── images"}]},{"ID":"20240723105824-wwnxkn8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240723105824-wwnxkn8","updated":"20240723105928"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"│   ├── train"}]},{"ID":"20240723105832-sdrrb2z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240723105832-sdrrb2z","updated":"20240723105928"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"│   └── val"}]},{"ID":"20240723105840-zaqwt49","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240723105840-zaqwt49","updated":"20240723105928"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"├── labels"}]},{"ID":"20240723105843-moamfjg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240723105843-moamfjg","updated":"20240724093958"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.2安装LabelImg打标签工具"}]},{"ID":"20240723110526-9od6sqd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240723110526-9od6sqd","updated":"20240723110540"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（打标签要后面打，先做处理图片的工作）"}]},{"ID":"20240723110203-oey9x88","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20240723110203-oey9x88","updated":"20240724093958"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.2.1.安装"}]},{"ID":"20240723110124-3473ihq","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240723110124-3473ihq","updated":"20240723110549"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"pip install -i https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple labelImg\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240723110417-ko1og2k","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240723110417-ko1og2k","updated":"20240724093958"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.处理图片"}]},{"ID":"20240723110625-ow7tmjv","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240723110625-ow7tmjv","updated":"20240724093958"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.1创建preprocess"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"images.py统一处理图片大小"}]},{"ID":"20240723110716-edbfy1i","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240723110716-edbfy1i","updated":"20240723111003"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"import cv2\nimport os\n\ndef preprocess_images(input_dir, output_dir):\n    if not os.path.exists(output_dir):\n        os.makedirs(output_dir)\n    for filename in os.listdir(input_dir):\n        if filename.endswith(\".jpeg\") or filename.endswith(\".png\"):\n            img = cv2.imread(os.path.join(input_dir, filename))\n            img = cv2.resize(img, (640, 640))  # 调整大小\n            output_path = os.path.join(output_dir, filename)\n            cv2.imwrite(output_path, img)\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    preprocess_images('../data/images/train', 'data/images/train_preprocessed')\n    preprocess_images('../data/images/val', 'data/images/val_preprocessed')\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240723111006-7ewofs4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240723111006-7ewofs4","updated":"20241104094227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.2打标签"}]},{"ID":"20240723111101-tfe3z1i","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20240723111101-tfe3z1i","updated":"20241104094227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.2.1启动 LabelImg："}]},{"ID":"20240723111211-730emf2","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240723111211-730emf2","updated":"20240723111228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240723111212-1rcs3ag","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240723111212-1rcs3ag","updated":"20240723111228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意：要用处理完大小的图片打标签"}]}]},{"ID":"20240723111101-og606hf","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240723111101-og606hf","updated":"20240723111108"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"在终端输入\nLabelImg\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240723122554-au6669v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240723122554-au6669v","updated":"20240723122554"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"20240723-122551"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/20240723-122551-20240723122554-9ui8l2j.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240724093940-ue172aq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240724093940-ue172aq","updated":"20241104094227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注：打的标签要存储到labels的文件夹中"}]},{"ID":"20240724093957-vi7ibpx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240724093957-vi7ibpx","updated":"20240724093958"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"20240724-093920"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/20240724-093920-20240724093958-9i6u2s3.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240723111123-s2ahs8h","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20240723111123-s2ahs8h","updated":"20240723122629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.2.2文件保存"}]},{"ID":"20240723111358-rpuhjwo","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240723111358-rpuhjwo","updated":"20240723111401"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240723111401-s1plybz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240723111401-s1plybz","updated":"20240723111401"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文件名保存为何图片原格式名字一样的文件名"}]}]},{"ID":"20240723111342-v3wmao5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240723111342-v3wmao5","updated":"20240723111342"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"20240723-111334"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/20240723-111334-20240723111342-91x2dsh.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240723111539-des1bov","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240723111539-des1bov","updated":"20241104094217"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.3data.yaml文件配置"}]},{"ID":"20241104094146-wifaq3n","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20241104094146-wifaq3n","updated":"20241104094217"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20241104094147-xl2jk3k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241104094147-xl2jk3k","updated":"20241104094217"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意：data.yaml中的train和val路径都要选择images下的"}]}]},{"ID":"20240723111553-tym46su","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240723111553-tym46su","updated":"20240723111606"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"train: data/images/train_preprocessed\nval: data/images/val_preprocessed\n\nnc: 2  # 类别数量\nnames: ['dirty', 'clean']  # 类别名称\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240723110654-7gxogq9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240723110654-7gxogq9","updated":"20240723122629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.4convert"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"labels.py将打完标签的xml格式文件转义为yolo的txt文件（打标签的时候选了yolo就不用再转换了）"}]},{"ID":"20240723110855-a7tb6q6","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240723110855-a7tb6q6","updated":"20240723122629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"import os\nimport xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n\ndef convert_voc_to_yolo(xml_file, output_path, classes):\n    try:\n        tree = ET.parse(xml_file)\n        root = tree.getroot()\n\n        size = root.find('size')\n        width = int(size.find('width').text)\n        height = int(size.find('height').text)\n\n        with open(output_path, 'w') as out_file:\n            for obj in root.iter('object'):\n                cls = obj.find('name').text\n                if cls not in classes:\n                    continue\n                cls_id = classes.index(cls)\n                xmlbox = obj.find('bndbox')\n                b = (float(xmlbox.find('xmin').text), float(xmlbox.find('xmax').text),\n                     float(xmlbox.find('ymin').text), float(xmlbox.find('ymax').text))\n                bb = (b[0] + b[1]) / 2.0 / width, (b[2] + b[3]) / 2.0 / height, (b[1] - b[0]) / width, (b[3] - b[2]) / height\n                out_file.write(f\"{cls_id} {' '.join(map(str, bb))}\\n\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"Error processing {xml_file}: {e}\")\n\ndef convert_dataset(voc_dir, yolo_dir, classes):\n    if not os.path.exists(yolo_dir):\n        os.makedirs(yolo_dir)\n    for filename in os.listdir(voc_dir):\n        if filename.endswith(\".xml\"):\n            xml_file = os.path.join(voc_dir, filename)\n            img_file = os.path.splitext(filename)[0] + '.jpeg'  # 根据实际图像格式修改\n            if os.path.exists(os.path.join(voc_dir, img_file)):\n                output_path = os.path.join(yolo_dir, os.path.splitext(filename)[0] + '.txt')\n                print(f\"Converting {xml_file} to {output_path}\")\n                convert_voc_to_yolo(xml_file, output_path, classes)\n            else:\n                print(f\"Image file {img_file} does not exist.\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    classes = [\"clean\", \"dirty\"]  # 根据实际类别名称修改\n    convert_dataset('../data/images/train_preprocessed', 'data/labels/train_preprocessed', classes)\n    convert_dataset('../data/images/val_preprocessed', 'data/labels/val_preprocessed', classes)\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240723110902-zy409bl","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240723110902-zy409bl","updated":"20241125101342"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.5train_yolo.py训练模型文件"}]},{"ID":"20240723111659-bpieuxd","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240723111659-bpieuxd","updated":"20240723111723"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"import os\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    os.system('python train.py --img 640 --batch 16 --epochs 50 --data data.yaml --weights yolov5s.pt')\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20241125101113-bxde1q8","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20241125101113-bxde1q8","updated":"20241125101342"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"# 注意！！！！！！ hyp参数一定要选择绝对路径 并且修改的参数不要写在data.yaml文件里 要写在对应指定的hyp的文件里，查看是否生效可以在run/trian/exp/hyp.yaml查看\n# --device 0,1表示用两块gpu训练\nimport os\n\nimport torch\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    os.system('python train.py --img 640 --batch 64   --epochs 100 --data data.yaml  --weights yolov5s.pt --hyp /home/Pinocchio/PythonProject/yolo_detect/yolov5-master/data/hyps/hyp.scratch-high.yaml --device 0,1 ')\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20241125101113-skll6x7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241125101113-skll6x7","updated":"20241125101113"}},{"ID":"20240723111724-9dk3ked","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240723111724-9dk3ked","updated":"20240723111810"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.6evaluate_yolo.py评估模型"}]},{"ID":"20240723111738-52l7ita","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240723111738-52l7ita","updated":"20240723111747"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"import os\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    # 评估模型\n    os.system('python val.py --weights runs/train/exp/weights/best.pt --data data.yaml --img 640')\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240723111748-57f1dl2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240723111748-57f1dl2","updated":"20240820160822"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.7detect_yolo.py推理模型"}]},{"ID":"20240723111759-259oodi","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240723111759-259oodi","updated":"20240723111809"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"import os\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    # 推理\n    os.system('python detect.py --weights runs/train/exp/weights/best.pt --img 640 --conf 0.25 --source data/images/val_preprocessed')\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240723111810-3gcir04","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240723111810-3gcir04","updated":"20240723111810"}},{"ID":"20240820160815-j2maq2b","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240820160815-j2maq2b","updated":"20240820161309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如何大批量自动标注"}]},{"ID":"20240820160825-yvqz0zf","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240820160825-yvqz0zf","updated":"20240820161228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240820160955-9xv8h8h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240820160955-9xv8h8h","updated":"20240820161002"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"参考这篇文章 https://www.cnblogs.com/cnZhi/articles/17055439.html"}]}]},{"ID":"20240820161228-iucysfp","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240820161228-iucysfp","updated":"20240820161309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.先自己手动打标签一批数据，然后训练，将训练好的权重保存好，即best.pt文件"}]},{"ID":"20240820161003-35ycif1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240820161003-35ycif1","updated":"20240821085116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.☆终端进入对应的yolo工程文件夹"}]},{"ID":"20240820161116-cqvse21","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240820161116-cqvse21","updated":"20240820161159"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240820161119-nkxg99r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240820161119-nkxg99r","updated":"20240820161159"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"找到detect.py文件 将store_true改为store_false"}]}]},{"ID":"20240820161201-ssttczw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240820161201-ssttczw","updated":"20240820161201"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240820161201-e32xprf.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240820161204-a094es9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240820161204-a094es9","updated":"20240820161604"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.创建文件夹用来存储想要自动打标签的图片"}]},{"ID":"20240820161321-b0q8r1e","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240820161321-b0q8r1e","updated":"20240820161350"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240820161339-uev2zno","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240820161339-uev2zno","updated":"20240820161350"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这里用more_person做例子"}]}]},{"ID":"20240820161351-3ravftv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240820161351-3ravftv","updated":"20240820161351"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240820161351-9m2d0rf.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240820161353-ldf429j","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240820161353-ldf429j","updated":"20240820161533"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"python .\\yolov5\\detect.py --weights .\\yolov5\\face_xth.pt --source .\\yolov5\\data\\more_person_face\\more_person_data\\\n\n# detect.py 为自带的文件\n# face_xth.pt为训练好的权重模型文件\n# .\\yolov5\\data\\more_person_face\\more_person_data\\为想要自动打标签的数据集图片\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240820161417-5k0sp45","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240820161417-5k0sp45","updated":"20240821084031"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.找到对应的detect的label"}]},{"ID":"20240820161606-8tb5wbc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240820161606-8tb5wbc","updated":"20240820161606"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240820161606-bc9f73t.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240820161617-iv48lfv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240820161617-iv48lfv","updated":"20240820161617"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240820161617-r715mrw.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240820161619-fsula1p","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240820161619-fsula1p","updated":"20240820171706"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240820161620-aa4m854","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240820161620-aa4m854","updated":"20240820171706"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将label中的txt和原图放在一个文件夹中，"}]},{"ID":"20240820161823-k8n6dpx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240820161823-k8n6dpx","updated":"20240820161912"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"然后新建classes.txt文件并将我们的训练标签id加进去，比如这里我的分类标签就一个xth，那就按下面的方式添加"}]},{"ID":"20240820161826-dvk91ex","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240820161826-dvk91ex","updated":"20240820161826"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"然后用labelimg进行查看并加工"}]}]},{"ID":"20240820161914-022kb55","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240820161914-022kb55","updated":"20240820161914"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240820161914-rp9coqs.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240821084010-rqkvogg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821084010-rqkvogg","updated":"20240821084010"}},{"ID":"20240821084012-i39srm0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240821084012-i39srm0","updated":"20240829144430"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如何在原来模型的基础上进一步训练"}]},{"ID":"20240821084034-sytvxfr","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240821084034-sytvxfr","updated":"20240821084923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240821084350-4gs8bgl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821084350-4gs8bgl","updated":"20240821084356"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先确认三个文件"}]},{"ID":"20240821084357-xsbjbdn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240821084357-xsbjbdn","updated":"20240821084923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821084406-aowg86i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240821084406-aowg86i","updated":"20240821084923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821084406-z2d8t87","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821084406-z2d8t87","updated":"20240821084923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"images文件夹 用来存放新的图像 要有训练集和测试集（注意，原来的图片不需要放了，只需要放最新要训练的图片）"}]}]},{"ID":"20240821084423-v5kpy5q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20240821084423-v5kpy5q","updated":"20240821084639"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821084423-uq3rl8a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821084423-uq3rl8a","updated":"20240821084639"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"labels文件夹 用来存放打完标签的txt文件以及图片，还有classes.txt文件 要有训练集和测试集"}]}]},{"ID":"20240821084453-y2qgk32","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20240821084453-y2qgk32","updated":"20240821084526"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240821084453-0fqt0h3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821084453-0fqt0h3","updated":"20240821084526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"data.yaml 引导训练路径以及训练格式"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240821084617-f43833d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821084617-f43833d","updated":"20240821084617"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240821084617-ytfxqo4.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240821084801-4t7sxek","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821084801-4t7sxek","updated":"20240821084805"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"训练代码"}]},{"ID":"20240821084805-2o14wi8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821084805-2o14wi8","updated":"20240821084805"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240821084805-hjlk8b8.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240821084643-el3u458","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240821084643-el3u458","updated":"20240829144430"}},{"ID":"20240821084929-gubq41t","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240821084929-gubq41t","updated":"20240828094455"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如何捕捉实时摄像头画面并截屏"}]},{"ID":"20240821085020-a47pn6e","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240821085020-a47pn6e","updated":"20240821085022"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"import cv2\nimport os\n\n# 设置摄像头索引（如果只有一个摄像头，通常为0）\ncam = cv2.VideoCapture(0)\n\n# 检查摄像头是否打开\nif not cam.isOpened():\n    print(\"无法打开摄像头\")\n    exit()\n\n# 保存照片的目录\nsave_dir = \"captured_images\"\n#save_dir = \"captured_val\"\nif not os.path.exists(save_dir):\n    os.makedirs(save_dir)\n\n# 初始化计数器\nimg_counter = 0\n\n# 检查目录中已存在的文件，找到最高编号\nexisting_files = [f for f in os.listdir(save_dir) if f.startswith(\"image_\") and f.endswith(\".jpg\")]\nif existing_files:\n    # 提取文件编号并找到最高编号\n    max_num = max([int(f.split('_')[1].split('.')[0]) for f in existing_files])\n    img_counter = max_num + 1\n\n# 目标比例为4:3\ntarget_aspect_ratio = 4 / 3\n#target_aspect_ratio = 1\n\nprint(\"按空格拍照，按q退出\")\n\nwhile True:\n    ret, frame = cam.read()\n    if not ret:\n        print(\"无法读取帧\")\n        break\n\n    # 获取当前帧的宽度和高度\n    height, width, _ = frame.shape\n\n    # 计算目标宽度和高度\n    target_width = width\n    target_height = int(target_width / target_aspect_ratio)\n\n    if target_height \u003e height:\n        # 如果计算的目标高度大于实际高度，则调整目标宽度\n        target_height = height\n        target_width = int(target_height * target_aspect_ratio)\n\n    # 中心裁剪图像\n    x_center = width // 2\n    y_center = height // 2\n\n    x_start = x_center - target_width // 2\n    y_start = y_center - target_height // 2\n\n    cropped_frame = frame[y_start:y_start + target_height, x_start:x_start + target_width]\n\n    # 显示实时视频流\n    cv2.imshow(\"Press Space to capture image\", cropped_frame)\n\n    # 等待用户输入\n    key = cv2.waitKey(1)\n\n    if key % 256 == 27:  # 按下Esc键退出\n        print(\"Esc 键被按下，退出...\")\n        break\n    elif key % 256 == 32:  # 按下空格键拍照\n        img_name = f\"{save_dir}/image_{img_counter:04d}.jpg\"\n        cv2.imwrite(img_name, cropped_frame)\n        print(f\"{img_name} 已保存\")\n        img_counter += 1\n    elif key == ord('q'):  # 按下q键退出\n        print(\"q 键被按下，退出...\")\n        break\n\n# 释放摄像头并关闭窗口\ncam.release()\ncv2.destroyAllWindows()\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240821085024-l7yne05","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240821085024-l7yne05","updated":"20240828094956"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"GTX1650显卡训练时出现NAN值怎么办"}]},{"ID":"20240828094506-2jh3vra","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240828094506-2jh3vra","updated":"20240828094506"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240828094507-iod03zy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240828094507-iod03zy","updated":"20240828094507"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240828094507-398cjp5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240828094507-398cjp5","updated":"20240828094609"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先检查data.yaml中的标签命名是否有问题"}]}]},{"ID":"20240828094609-eb7hghu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20240828094609-eb7hghu","updated":"20240828094609"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240828094609-evzhcx4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240828094609-evzhcx4","updated":"20240828094632"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"检查labels文件夹中的classes.txt文件的标签名是否正确 对应"}]}]},{"ID":"20240828094632-6cj7gug","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20240828094632-6cj7gug","updated":"20240828094632"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240828094632-pphqcxp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240828094632-pphqcxp","updated":"20240828094729"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果上述都正确，则是16xx显卡的问题，需要将yolo文件夹中的train.py文件中的amp进行修改"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240828094824-t8xx3my","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240828094824-t8xx3my","updated":"20240828094911"},"Children